==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Roper
<hw>Rop"er</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>A maker of
ropes.</def> <rj><au>P. Plowman.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>One who ropes goods; a packer.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>3.</sn> <def>One fit to be hanged.</def> <mark>[Old Slang]</mark>
<rj><au>Douce.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Ropery</ent>⟦br⟧
